{"tid":1373771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家需唔需要每日一報做整合, 方便文宣同做所有人既懶人包???","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T03:16:59.000Z","uid":112391,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1bf59443f2c404c4bc5ae87a2ad33790547caf02","tid":1373771,"uid":112391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:15:50.000Z","msg":"如題, 其實大家需唔需要每次活動做一次總結, 整合全日發生既所有事?大至舉旗有衝突, 小至口角屌老母<br />\n呢個幾月見到好多手足好有心每日做好多文宣工作, 想比更多人睇到衝突雙方既發生經過, 或者被捕幾多手足, 再者開左幾多槍有幾多彈殼然後記者會9up左d咩, 咁如果每日一篇咁做積少成多係咪會容易好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實內容係類似新聞, 但個分別係呢到可以包含埋各手足得出黎既結論(eg今日727前線對&quot;撤退共識&quot;既不滿), 同時亦可以每日keep住更新, 將來清算某d condom都可以拎番當日既post同source 做證據(例如香蕉糖, 牙wave既post係咪已經沉左?)<br />\n<br />\n第一次開post 唔好屌咁大力<br />\n如果唔認同既就請負皮+由個post沉"},{"pid":"52c968690e6d932305a54aa32f2c7821fb6eeaa2","tid":1373771,"uid":112391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:20:55.000Z","msg":"推你老母"},{"pid":"dfd110eb7186ef25a65a74ff2e0fce17b054a5b7","tid":1373771,"uid":112391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:31:57.000Z","msg":"推佢老母"},{"pid":"d1c6dcc5367fa46d8df8aca8998cbbe0f85f6827","tid":1373771,"uid":112391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"推狗老母"},{"pid":"f2b162871ce9a9aa0a32a9efa7cf7b871ae34211","tid":1373771,"uid":112391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:57:08.000Z","msg":"推貓老母"},{"pid":"a1017e6381fdfb57073ee484b1599bd137d30fd6","tid":1373771,"uid":286285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wn8z59W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwn8z59W.png&h=0e97fc0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/diMRoWC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdiMRoWC.png&h=2be708f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://n